---
title: Golden Chicken & Garlic Kumara Mash with Dill & Parsley Dressing
description: This take on meat and three veg has just enough little tricks to transform your regular dinner into a family favourite. The garlicky
kumara mash and herby mayo are out of this world!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/aussie-chicken-garlic-kumara-mash-6033862f.jpg
